 * # The path of Moon.
 *
 * Goes as follows:
 *
 * Moonlight Troupe
 * Grasp of Lunacy
 * Smile of the moon
 * > Sidepaths:
 *   Mind Gate
 *   Ashen Eyes
 *
 * Mark of Moon
 * Ritual of Knowledge
 * Lunar Parade
 * Moonlight Amulet
 * > Sidepaths:
 *   Curse of Paralasys
 *   Unfathomable Curio
 * 	 Unsealed Arts
 *
 * Moonlight blade
 * Ringleaders Rise
 * > Sidepaths:
 *   Ashen Ritual
 *
 * Last Act
 */
